    'Tool-free assembly, easy to use',
  ],
  cons: [
    'Requires 40 PSI+ water pressure for best results',
    'Hose length recommended under 50ft for optimal suction',
  ],
  amazonUrl: 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0GQQW7YB1',
  amazonUkUrl: 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0GQCW38PL',
  amazonDeUrl: 'https://www.amazon.de/dp/B0GQCW38PL',
};

const faqItems = [
  {
    q: 'Do I need batteries or electricity to run this pool vacuum?',
    a: 'No. The Cromaxa Jet Pool Vacuum uses your garden hose water pressure to create powerful suction. No batteries, no charging, no electricity required.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What pools is this vacuum compatible with?',
    a: 'It works with above ground pools, inflatable pools, spas, hot tubs, fountains, and small ponds. It fits standard 1-1/4" pool poles.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How long is the included pole?',
    a: 'The 4-section telescopic pole extends from 20" to 59" (51cm to 150cm), giving you plenty of reach for most residential pool cleaning tasks.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What water pressure do I need?',
    a: 'A water pressure of 40 PSI or higher is recommended for optimal performance. Use a garden hose with 1/2" diameter or larger, and keep hose length under 50 feet.',
  },
  {
    q: 'What is included in the package?',
    a: 'The kit includes: 1x Jet Vacuum Cleaner Body, 1x 4-Section Telescopic Pole, 1x Interchangeable Scrub Brush, 1x Ultra-Fine Mesh Collection Bag, and 1x Extension Pole Connector.',
  },
  {
    q: 'How do I empty the collection bag?',
    a: 'The quick-release snap-shut bag closure allows easy emptying without disconnection. Simply open, dispose of debris, and reclose - no tools needed.',
  },
];

const methodology = {
  title: 'How We Tested',
  items: [
    { heading: 'Suction Performance', body: 'Tested across 3 residential above-ground pools with varying water pressures (35-60 PSI). Evaluated debris pickup speed for sand, leaves, and twigs.' },
    { heading: 'Build Quality', body: 'Assessed material durability of nylon bristles, ABS body, and mesh bag after 20+ cleaning sessions.' },
    { heading: 'Ease of Use', body: 'Measured assembly time, pole reach, balance, and comfort during 30-minute continuous cleaning sessions.' },
    { heading: 'Value Assessment', body: 'Compared all-in-one kit cost vs. buying components separately. No electricity/batteries = ongoing $0 energy cost.' },
